Regression analysis to see relationship between AQI and distance

Rush hour: weekdays, 7 ~ 10 am Non-Rush hour: weekdays, 4 ~ 7 am buffer distance = 800 m calculate the nearby outdoor AQI change percentage Regression between outdoor AQI change percentage and distance from nearest highway filter the outdoor AQI change percentage > 0 and outdoor AQI change percentage < 50

Group by sensors. Average their outdoor AQI change percentage in the past month. For all the nearby outdoor sensors (167), do regression: \[log(outdoor\ AQI\ change\ percentage) = a_1 \times distance\ from\ nearest\ highway + a_0\]
